Nibbles
=======

Nibbles is a snake game for single player, or multiplayer on a single machine
or across multiple machines via TCP.  It is inspired by the Basic game of
the same name.

Copyright (C) 2010  John Bytheway <jbytheway at that gmail place>

For building instructions see INSTALL.


